						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-4 text-center">Insufficient Heat</h3>
					<p class="text-darkgray mb-4">
						If your furnace is running but not producing enough heat, it could be due to a clogged filter, improper
						thermostat settings, or issues with the pilot light or ignition system. Our technicians can diagnose the
						problem and restore proper heating to your home.
					</p>
				</div>

				<!-- Strange Noises -->
				<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
					<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-secondary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
