						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-4 text-center">Strange Noises</h3>
					<p class="text-darkgray mb-4">
						Banging, rattling, whistling, or grinding noises from your furnace often indicate mechanical problems such
						as loose components, airflow restrictions, or worn-out parts. Our team can identify the source of the noise
						and make necessary repairs.
					</p>
				</div>

				<!-- Frequent Cycling -->
