						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-4 text-center">Ignition Problems</h3>
					<p class="text-darkgray mb-4">
						Issues with the pilot light or electronic ignition system can prevent your furnace from starting. Our
						technicians can repair or replace faulty ignition components to ensure reliable furnace operation.
					</p>
				</div>

				<!-- Blower Motor Issues -->
				<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
