						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-4 text-center">Blower Motor Issues</h3>
					<p class="text-darkgray mb-4">
						Problems with the blower motor can result in poor airflow, uneven heating, or a furnace that won't start.
						Our team can repair or replace faulty blower motors to restore proper system function.
